  <brief_title>Comparison Between the Clinical Assessment of the Undescended Testis and Its' Ultrasonographic Size</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison Between the Clinical Assessment of the Undescended Testis and Its' Ultrasonographic Size</official_title>
  <sponsors>
